title: The video surveillance market is expected to grow from USD 48.7billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 76.4billion by 2027; it is expected to grow at a CAGR of 9.4%
The vaccine adjuvants market is projected to reach USD 1.6 Billion by 2027 from USD 1.5 Billion in 2022, at a CAGR of 1.7%
